TextArea_SetSelection
#include Style
#Background wimp 1
Module:	<TextGadgets=>textgadgets/m>
#Line
#Wrap off
Veneer:	<textarea_set_selection>
Syntax:	TextArea_SetSelection
#indent

On entry:
#indent 6
{FCode}r0 = flags
r1 = window object Id
r2 = 0x4018 + 7 (16415)
r3 = gadget component Id
r4 = <start index=>textarea_special_index_values>
r5 = <end index=>textarea_special_index_values>
{f}
#indent
On exit:
#indent 6
{FCode}r1-r9 preserved
{f}
#indent
#Wrap
Purpose:	Method selects (highlights) the text between positions R4 and R5 within a text area.